.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, july, january, december, february
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, weightlifting, sailing
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, airplane, train, helicopter, tram
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: novembermaster, romance, animation, mystery, documentary
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, amaryllis, daisy, poppy, tulip
1. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's birthday is in january
2. the person who's sport is swedish is the person who growsdaisy
3. the person who's sport is basketball is the person driving the helicopter
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december
5. the person who's birthday is in july is the person driving the airplane
6. the person watching animation movies is the person who growsamaryllis
7. the person who's birthday is in february is the person watching romance movies
8. the person driving the train is in the middle
9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left
10. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person who growslily
11. the person who growstulips is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies
12. the person watching novembermaster movies is the person driving the bus
13. the person who's sport is cricket is the person watching mystery movies
14. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november
15. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person driving the tram

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Birthday		|    february	|     november	|      january	|     july	|     december	|
| Sport	|   weightlifting	|    basketball	|    baseball	|    cricket	|    swedish	|
| Flower		|     lily	|    tulip	|     amaryllis	|     poppy	|      daisy	|
| Transport	|    tram	|     helicopter	|     train	|    airplane	|      bus	|
| Movie-Genre		|   romance	|    documentary	|  animation	|    mystery	|   novembermaster	|
